@startuml
title Participant-to-Host Inputs and Emoji
hide footbox
autonumber

skinparam BackgroundColor transparent
skinparam SequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam MaxMessageSize 110
skinparam WrapWidth 220
skinparam RoundCorner 8

actor "Participant browser\nstatic/participant.js" as Participant
participant "Railway upload router" as UploadRailway
participant "Daemon misc router" as MiscAPI
participant "Daemon emoji router" as EmojiAPI
participant "Daemon upload handler" as UploadDaemon
participant "Host browser" as Host
participant "Desktop overlay\naddons bridge" as Overlay
participant "Email notifications" as Email

group Paste text to host
Participant -> MiscAPI: POST /api/participant/paste
MiscAPI -> MiscAPI: add_paste(uuid, text)
MiscAPI -> Host: host_event paste_received
end

group Feedback email
Participant -> MiscAPI: POST /api/participant/misc/feedback
MiscAPI -> Email: send feedback email with session + participant name
Email --> MiscAPI: accepted
end

group File upload handoff
Participant -> UploadRailway: POST /{session}/api/upload (multipart + uuid)
UploadRailway -> UploadRailway: stream temp file to .server-data/uploads
UploadRailway -> UploadDaemon: daemon WS push file_ready_for_download

UploadDaemon -> UploadRailway: GET /upload/{file_id} (host-auth download)
UploadRailway --> UploadDaemon: temp file bytes
UploadDaemon -> UploadDaemon: save file into session_folder/uploads
UploadDaemon -> UploadRailway: daemon WS send_to_host file_uploaded
UploadRailway -> Host: forward file_uploaded to host WS
UploadDaemon -> UploadRailway: POST /upload/{file_id}/ack {disk_path}
UploadRailway -> UploadRailway: delete Railway temp file

opt Host dismisses the upload indicator
  Host -> MiscAPI: POST /host/uploads/seen
  MiscAPI -> MiscAPI: mark uploaded file as seen
end
end

group Emoji reaction
Participant -> EmojiAPI: POST /api/participant/emoji/reaction
EmojiAPI -> Overlay: send_emoji best-effort over addons bridge
EmojiAPI -> Host: notify_host emoji_reaction
end
@enduml
